  "text": "The coupling constants g \u03b3 \u01eb\u00b5 represent 18 independent real parameters, so it is not possible to determine all of them from the existing muon decay observables. A global analysis of all the existing muon decay measurements can nonetheless set stringent model-independent experimental limits on the non-standard model contributions [4, 9, [CITATION_1] 11] that can then be compared to model calculations such as those in [12] , which predict that g S,V,T LR and g",
